divs: Sighting Details8pm Moore, oklahoma. went outside to smoke. Saw an orange light moving from the SW to the NE, moving towards me. It was moving about 100mph and its elevation was about 500 to 1500 ft. As it passed over it made no sound and it was orange and slightly pulsating and glowing.
Summary: Pulsating orange oval light traveling sw to ne
